===Etymology 3===
From {{inh|ru|sla-pro|*o(b)}}, from {{inh|ru|ine-pro|*h₃ebʰi}}.

====Pronunciation====
* {{audio|Ru-о.ogg|Audio (stressed)|lang=ru}}
* {{qualifier|stressed}} {{ru-IPA}}
* {{qualifier|directly preceding the stress}} {{ru-IPA-manual|[ɐ]}}
* {{qualifier|unstressed, in other positions}} {{ru-IPA-manual|[ə]}}

====Preposition====
{{head|ru|preposition}}

# (+ [[prepositional case]]) [[about]], [[of]], [[on]]
#: {{uxi|ru|[[я|Я]] [[читать|чита́л]] о [[он|нём]]|I’ve read about him.}}
# {{lb|ru|literary}} (+ [[accusative case]]) [[against]], [[upon]]
#: {{uxi|ru|[[опира́ться]] о [[стена|сте́ну]]|to lean against the wall}}

====Pronunciation and usage notes====
* The ''о'' form is unstressed except in the idiom [[бок о бок|бок о́‎ бок]].
* When governing the prepositional case, the form ''о'' is used before consonants, expect before a few clusters where the form ''обо'' is used.
* When governing the accusative, the form ''о'' is used before most consonants in the written language: the usage is variable before liquids. In the spoken language, ''об'' is used in all cases.

====Alternative forms====
* {{l|ru|об}} {{qualifier|before vowels and in some other cases}}
* {{l|ru|обо}} {{qualifier|before some words such as ''мне'' or ''все''}}

